{"tid":836243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一地兩檢黨就香港共產黨成立一事發表聲明","createTime":"2018-09-25T13:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T03:28:07.000Z","uid":35699,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e928e5d95dd35cee1da2262ab7edd6bca156934e","tid":836243,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/213238_a6dd1c7851f53cd1f5c818b5a0cdfac5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F213238_a6dd1c7851f53cd1f5c818b5a0cdfac5.png&h=e84a3a50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聲明全文：<br />\n<br />\n一地兩檢黨草創一日多，悉香港共產黨於同日成立，立場與本黨大相逕庭，本黨對其反人類立場表示憤慨。香港共產黨有可能為中國共產黨於香港的正式分支，一地兩檢黨會將香港共產黨視為中華人民共和國的執政黨，當香港成立國家之時，將命令香港共產黨負責人清除所有於香港工作的共產黨成員，並停止其於香港的活動。<br />\n<br />\n至於西九龍站的中華人民共和國領地，一地兩檢黨領導下的新政府將永久割讓予香港共產黨統治的中華人民共和國，並將對其實施的反人類政綱不聞不問。<br />\n<br />\n【完】"},{"pid":"975ecf9643edb46881212051358c6949889d5494","tid":836243,"uid":143499,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:15:54.000Z","msg":"高登啲痴線佬終於放曬出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登真係好少人有高登嗰種質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5805006615b9d5efb9de6ad358320788c26aa1","tid":836243,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:33:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d494b30a86ed74ed4c51ed4f1d1e2e051dc67f9","tid":836243,"uid":1655,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:40:14.000Z","msg":"當年侵侵都俾人話佢癲，而家撚到支那一棟都冇<br />\n支持癲佬治國<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c499083c44f2589ebc09a16cd27d7a1843ebf0c8","tid":836243,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:44:17.000Z","msg":"集思廣益 仲有冇其他黨可以成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmo